value: Breeding visitor and Palearctic winter visitor, near water: breeding visitor SE Morocco - Algeria, patchy Mauritania coast, L Chad area wintering across West Africa S of Sahara north of forest (chrysocercus); breeds Nile Delta (and Middle East and parts of Asia) wintering E Sudan - Somalia south to S Angola - NE South Africa (persicus).
